  <description>
    <ul>
      <li>Fast-paced tactical action. Control the movement of all your forces at the same time</li>
      <li>Simple yet original game mechanics, discovered by Thomas Colcombet</li>
      <li>10 different teams, each with their own charactaristics and special attacks</li>
      <li>13 levels, each one twisting the gameplay in a new direction</li>
      <li>100+ more levels if you download the bonus pack</li>
      <li>Levels can be created using simple image files</li>
      <li>Lots of level design options: walls, edge wraparound, bridges, different speed, special areas such as glue or danger and varied army size and fighter behavior</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
